creator: Noble Health App
descriptionHtml:
We believe that the greatest outcomes are made possible through between-session support.

App Features/Benefits
––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––

Self-guided Roadmaps on a Variety of Topics:

Our Roadmaps are therapist-created, research-backed, and designed to provide the tools individuals need to experience healing. Roadmaps allow individuals to do foundational work between sessions that will help them get the most out of one-on-one sessions with their mental health professional and experience greater improvement in less time.

Format That Teaches “Consistency Over Time”:

Our “bite-size” daily content format helps individuals learn the art of staying consistent in their journey for the long haul. Recovery and healing are marathons, not sprints, and should be worked at slowly and consistently over time for the best results.

Assessments to Track Progress:

Regular check-ins in each section of our Roadmaps help allow individuals to stay present in their journey, monitor their progress, and pinpoint areas that they may need to work on more with their mental health professional.

Coming Soon
––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––

– Push Notifications
– Native App Video Calls
– A.I. Based Suggestions
– Clinical and Self Assessments
– Design Update

Learn more: www.noble.health

title: Noble.

creator: Noble Health App
descriptionHtml:
Noble’s Remote Therapeutic Monitoring program offers a systemic approach by connecting the patient, a Noble Coach, and a care provider (when applicable, not required) for a more complete mental health solution.

Remote Therapeutic Monitoring has been shown to:
––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––
Reduce healthcare costs
Reduce therapy visits
Reduce doctors visits
Improve diagnosis
Improve outcomes
Increase continuity of care

Offering a true understanding of mental health through:
––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––
Subjective data from self-reported assessments
Daily mood check-ins
Objective health data from wearables (coming soon)
Continual monitoring of client status

An accessible, connection-focused approach to care:
––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––
Weekly face-to-face CBT (Cognitive Behavioral Therapy) sessions with a Noble Coach
App-based Treatment Protocol Roadmap (daily video and audio content, reflection questions, and more)
Goal setting, communication, and support

What clients are saying about our program:
––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––
“I cannot tell you the tremendous improvement in myself that I have experienced using this program.”
“I feel more awareness than I’ve felt in a long time. Good grief… I’m noticing real change and real awareness! It’s wonderful.”
“I am feeling lighter and happier than I have for a very long time.”
“I am seeing change in my life. I'm feeling less fear.”

Updates in this release:
• Tell us how you’re feeling! Our new daily mood check-in feature offers you a quick way to share how you’re feeling and track your progress over time.
• You now have greater insight into your progress! We have added a health data tab to the client dashboard, offering you anytime access to your clinical assessment results and previously logged moods, as well as insight into your progress and compliance with your program.
• An elevated user experience, because you’re worth it. When you log into the app you will notice an updated home screen dashboard with a smoother navigation layout, making your weekly calls and Roadmaps easier to find and navigate!

creator: Noble Health App
descriptionHtml:
At Noble, we understand that life's challenges can feel overwhelming. That's why we connect you with certified cognitive-behavioral coaches who are here to provide the support and tools you need. Whether you're battling stress, anxiety, relationship issues, or simply seeking personal growth, Noble offers compassionate guidance tailored to your unique circumstances. Take steps towards improving your mental health, developing stronger coping skills and relationships, finding motivation, and achieving lasting behavior change.

Noble clients have access to:
- Virtual cognitive behavioral coaching sessions
- Goal setting and tracking
- Assessments
- Anytime messaging
- Educational video courses

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: Introducing Plans! This new feature is designed to propel you forward with relevant, personalized goals and action items. Collaborate with your coach to create custom daily or weekly objectives and actionable steps, which you can access anytime in our app or on the web.
